data.meta_description: Find out how to watch The Legend of White Fang. Stream the latest seasons and episodes, watch trailers, and more for The Legend of White Fang at TV Guide
data.text:
1992-1992

1 Season

Family Channel

Watchlist

Animated adventures for young children about a dog and the girl who befriends him, based on the Jack London story set in the Yukon during the gold rush of the 1890s. A French-Canadian coproduction.
